Tensor is a data structure-->a way of storing data.
ML library(sklearn,tensorflow)-->use the ds of tensor.
Tensor is used in ML and DL.
Google-ML lib-->Tensorflow-->Name placed on tensor.
Tensor is a container for storing numbers.(sometimes we store characters and string also but rarely)

Vectors and matrices are basically tensors-->if they are of 0 dimension then they are scalers.
list->vector
2D->matrix
3D and above->Tensors

Axis of a tensor=dimension of the tensor=rank

